metadata.title: Where can I download the user’s guide for RH850/F1K group. I am not able to find the data sheet from renesas Site?

sections.content:
Question:
Where can I download the user’s guide for RH850/F1K group. I am not able to find the data sheet from renesas Site? 
Answer:
Please choose the device family for which you want documentation under the HIGHLIGHTED PRODUCTS section of: https://www.renesas.com/us/en/products/automotive.html. From there, you can find data sheets, application notes and software under the Documents or Software sections along the top.
Suitable Products
RH850/F1x
